# Notes
# 1. You can place this file at the repo root as `.env`, or create `server/.env`.
# 2. `server/index.js` now reads `server/.env` first, then falls back to the repo root `.env`.
# 3. Confirm the local Kingbase/PostgreSQL port and credentials before starting the server.
